(6226297, 'wcst_template_messages', 'a:5:{s:17:\"wcst_mail_message\";s:3725:\"<span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">Örömmel értesítünk, hogy rendelésedet összekészítettük, és átadtuk a</span><br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">futárszolgálatnak. Hamarosan megérkezik hozzád!</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Nyomonkövetéshez szükséges követőkód: #</strong>[tracking_number]\r\n<a class=\\\"wcst_tracking_link\\\" href=\\\"[url_track]\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"><strong>Ide kattintva</strong></a> eléred a nyomonkövetési oldalát.\r\nA csomag elküldve: [dispatch_date]<br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">A futárszolgálat hamarosan kapcsolatba lép veled a kézbesítés pontos</span><br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">idejével kapcsolatban. Ha kérdésed lenne, bátran vedd fel velünk a</span><br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">kapcsolatot az alábbi elérhetőségeken:</span>\r\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.21575rem; color: #222222; font-family: Inter;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\\\">Mobil:</span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\\\"> 06 (30) 478 8101</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.21575rem; color: #222222; font-family: Inter;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\\\">Információ: </span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\\\">info@chilimania.hu</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: #222222; font-family: Inter;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\\\">Cím: </span><a style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; touch-action: manipulation; color: #ff424e; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: 0.75px; transition: color 0.2s; margin-bottom: 0px; text-underline-offset: 0.12em;\\\" href=\\\"https://goo.gl/maps/kbSLSrMjwh1YvQJS8\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: inherit;\\\">1136 Budapest Hegedűs Gyula utca 32.</span></a></p>\r\n<br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">Köszönjük, hogy nálunk vásároltál!</span><br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">Üdvözlettel,</span><br style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\" /><span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\">Chilimánia</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\"> </span>\r\n<div class=\\\"yj6qo\\\" style=\\\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: large;\\\"></div>\";s:38:\"wcst_mail_message_additional_shippings\";s:158:\"<img class=\\\"aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"https://chilimania.hu/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/cropped-cropped-chilimania_piros-e1726907751230.png\\\" alt=\\\"Chilimánia\\\" />\";s:50:\"wcst_active_notification_text_before_tracking_info\";s:0:\"\";s:31:\"wcst_order_details_page_message\";s:10:\"<h3>.</h3>\";s:44:\"wcst_order_details_page_additional_shippings\";s:1:\".\";}', 'yes'),
